---
title: Sri Lankan-Spiced Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Lime Mayo & Almonds
description: This dish comes with a big juicy warning - it’s too delicious to refuse! Be lured to the table when you get a good wiff of the juicy chicken, marinated in Sri Lankan spices. Combined with roasted root veggies and a zesty mayo, this dish will have you running back for seconds in no time.
